Web based system that integrates with the Harvard video courses. Content 
from their site is stored locally and presented for UVA students who can 
login withtheir UVA login, and once logged in dicuss below the videos. 
Teachers have moderative permissions.

Installing
----------
You need a MySQL database and PHP5+ running to install LearnScape. After
uploading these files to your server, open /include/config.php and ensure 
that the constants defined there are correct (see the comments there for
instructions). When these are filled in correctly, go to your website in a
webbrowser. You will be asked wether to automatically install the required
databasei tables. After this step is completed, your site is running!

* // make sure extension=php_openssl.dll is added to php.ini in order to make this work


